body_html: @rockyrhodes thanks for the reply. Yes, I guess another way to phrase it would be, when will Android and TensorFlow support acceleration on Qualcomm chips that leverages the Hexagon DSP. It was mentioned in the TF Summit 2018 that it would come in Android P.
